  
2.0.0 (20140228) : 
	First revision of this revision history.

2.0.1 (20140303) : 
	Print log for version number.
	
2.0.2 (20140311) : 
	Update FW version to P46.

2.0.3 (20140407) :
	Update FW version to P47.
	Add ROM patch checking mechanism.

2.0.4 (20140520) : 
    Set low power mode.

2.0.5 (20140529) : 
    Add new define value : BT_REDUCE_EP2_POLLING_INTERVAL_BY_INTR

2.0.6 (20140531) : 
	Add new feature : read driver version from ioctl.
2.0.7 (20140610) : 
	Update ROM patch  version to P53

2.0.8 (20140712) : 
    Update ROM patch version to P54
    Add new feature : read driver probe counter

2.0.9 (20140818) : 
    Send HCI command before suspend.
    Reduce ROM patch file loading time.

2.0.10 (20140904) : 
    Bug fix for MT7632

2.0.11 (20140929) : 
    Send HCI_RESET when no need to load rom patch.

2.0.12 (20141001) : 
	Add FW assert log dump mechanism.
	
2.0.13 (20141016) : 
    Improve FW assert log dump mechanism to support large file size.
    
2.0.14 (20141017) : 
    To support Linux kernel 3.13.
    Finetune FW dump log & file name.

2.0.15 (20141027) : 
    To support dongle reset when intialization failed.
    To support FW assert UI.

2.0.16 (20141117) : 
    Finetune HW rst pin toggle mechanism.
    Sync BT driver for SCO.

2.0.17 (20141121) :
    Support HCI CMD filter for unpredicted command.

2.0.18 (20141126) :
    Support send dummy bulk out packet after resume.

2.0.19 (20141203) : 
    Add mechanism : force kernek panic when FW assert.
    Add mechanism : new ioctl to get dongle reset status.
    Add mechanism : new ioctl to force dongle reset.

2.0.20 (20141216) : 
	Add debug log.
	Add HCI dump mechanism.
	Set control trnafer timeout value to 100ms.

2.0.21 (20141223) : 
	Finetune error handling for btmtk_usb_close.

2.0.22 (20141224) : 
    Fine-tune log.    
    Enable BT low power mode.

2.0.23 (20141226) : 
    Add FW log mechanism.

2.0.24 (20141229) : 
    Add new API for wifi driver to trigger FW assert core dump.

2.0.25 (20150108) : 
    Add new mechanism : keep hci dev instance.

2.0.26 (20150109) : 
    Add new mechanism : send dummy error hci event after resume.

2.0.27 (20150113) : 
    Debugging for the new mechanisms.

2.0.28 (20150114) : 
    Add ioctl to qurery suspend/resume status.

2.0.29 (20150114) : 
    Improve error handling.

2.0.30 (20150121) : 
    Add error handling for HCI_RESET command failed.

2.0.31 (20150127) : 
	Add new API to set rom patch version string.

2.0.32 (20150129) : 
    Increase probe counter in suspend function instead of probe function.

2.0.33 (20150205) :
    Update probe_counter behavior.

2.0.34 (20150206) : 
    Update wake up reason checking.

2.0.35 (20150212) :
    Support reduce EP2 BULK_IN polling by INTERRUPT_IN.

2.0.36 (20150216) :
    Fix suspend/resume timing issue.

2.0.36 (20150225) :
